To ensure the database integrate well with the code.
Use:
database name = mippsy
table name = user, Posts

user table contains
    id (int, auto increment, primary key)
    email (varchar, email)
    password (varchar)
    join_date (datetime)


Posts table contains
    id (int, auto increment, primary key)
    fname (varchar)
    lname (varchar)
    age (int)
    gender (varchar)
    date (datetime)   // time which post is created
    contactNumber (varchar)
    additionalInfo (varchar)
    emailAddress (varchar, email)
    userID (int)
